high_descs: Move to the left of the wooden dresser.
Pick up the pencil that is on the farther side of the dresser.
Turn around and walk forward and then to the desk on your left.
Put the pencil down on the desk.
Turn around and walk forward and then back to the dresser on the right.
Pick up the other pencil on the dresser.
Turn around and walk back to the desk on your left.
Set the pencil down on the left opposite to the other pencil.
anns.task_desc: Move both pencils on the dresser over to the desk.

high_descs: Turn to the left and take a step before turning back to the table.
Pick up the pen closest to the mirror next to the coffee cup.
Turn around ad walk toward the door.  Turn left at the door and walk toward the desk.
Put the pen down on the desk to the right of the pen in front of the desk chair.
Turn around and walk toward the wall, turn right in the middle of the room and walk toward the dresser.
Pick up the pen on the dresser.
Turn around and walk toward the door.  Turn left at the door and walk toward the desk.
Put the pen down to the left of the other two pens.
anns.task_desc: Moved two pens from the dresser to the desk.

high_descs: Move to the left side of the dresser.
Pick up the pencil to the left of the white mug.
Turn around and walk to the door, take a left at the door, walk to the desk ahead.
Put the pencil down to the left of the cell phone closest to the lap top.
Turn around and walk back to the dresser.
Pick up the pencil next to the keys.
Walk back over to the desk.
Put the pencil down to the right of the alarm clock.
anns.task_desc: To move two pencils to the desk.
